Invocation Name: my workout routine
des:
Work out with Alexa throughout the week. Once you open the skill, just ask Alexa to start the workout. You can also ask Alexa for your progress.
Up to 50 workouts to choose from and use. Good luck!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
